OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774555873
OL,3,C'Reckless' arsonist set fire in
OL,4,Cresidential block before assaulting
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FA "reckless" arsonist who started a
OL,8,Ffire in a residential block in Kent
OL,9,Fhas been jailed.
OL,11,FAmie Bray deliberately started the
OL,12,Fblaze in her home in Copenhagen Road
OL,13,Fin Gillingham at about 11pm on 5 May
OL,14,Flast year.
OL,16,FPolice were called to the scene and
OL,17,Fwhile the 32-year-old was being
OL,18,Fdetained, she kicked an officer.
OL,20,FShe later slapped another officer
OL,21,Fwhile she was being put in a cell.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
