FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774555873
OL,3,C'Reckless' arsonist set fire in
OL,4,Cresidential block before assaulting
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FBray was charged with arson being
OL,8,Freckless as to whether lives were
OL,9,Fendangered and two counts of
OL,10,Fassaulting an officer in the execution
OL,11,Fof their duty.
OL,13,FBray was remanded in custody until she
OL,14,Fpleaded guilty at Maidstone Crown
OL,15,FCourt on Friday 20 March 2026.
OL,17,FShe was sentenced to 28 months in
OL,18,Fprison for the arson and two months
OL,19,Fconcurrent for the assaults on
OL,20,Fconstables.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
