OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774555873
OL,3,C'Reckless' arsonist set fire in
OL,4,Cresidential block before assaulting
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FBray has been jailed for a further
OL,8,Fyear for breaching a suspended
OL,9,Fsentence order, with a total custodial
OL,10,Fsentence of 40 months.
OL,12,FInvestigating officer, Detective
OL,13,FSergeant Emily Matthews, said: "Bray's
OL,14,Freckless attempt to deliberately cause
OL,15,Fa fire in her flat put other
OL,16,Fresidents' lives at risk, and it is
OL,17,Fright that she should face the
OL,18,Fconsequences of her actions.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
