PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774555873
OL,3,C'Reckless' arsonist set fire in
OL,4,Cresidential block before assaulting
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,F"Fires can quickly get out of control
OL,8,Fin any setting, but especially so in a
OL,9,Fblock of flats at night when other
OL,10,Fpeople may be asleep. Her neighbours
OL,11,Fwill certainly feel safer now she is
OL,12,Fbehind bars."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
